FBIS4-36275 "drnes110_j_94003" FBIS-NES-94-110 Daily Report 8 Jun 1994 ARABIAN PENINSULA Yemen Salih Telephone Conversation With Sector Commander Cited Salih Telephone Conversation With Sector Commander Cited PM0806131294 London AL-SHARQ AL-AWSAT in Arabic 8 Jun 94 p 1 PM0806131294 London AL-SHARQ AL-AWSAT Arabic BFN ["Text" of telephone conversation between President Salih and unidentified Tawr al-Bahah sector commander; place and date not given] [Text] Salih: You are working like a tortoise, not mechanized units...the mission has to be accomplished quickly, because time is money...time is money...time is money. Sector commander: We request a delay for a few hours, because the situation is a tortoise situation, and we are working to coordinate. Salih: Accomplish the mission, there should be no stumbling blocks in your way...this is what is important, and do not listen to anything, because it is designed for the outside, not the inside.
